            <scopecontent id="aspace_78ef4ae0a5965de0d312745a19f0a21d">
               <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
               <p>This series contains Bennett's personal and professional correspondence reflecting her career and personal relationships. Most notably the series contains letters from Langston Hughes (some of which include poetry) and correspondence between Bennett and her parents. The letters between Bennett and her parents are particularly rich and contain insight into Bennett's experience as a writer and artist.</p>
